UID:stream-22842211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260309T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260404T213100Z
DTSTART:20260330T203000Z
DTEND:20260330T223000Z
SUMMARY:Euro Truck Simulator 2 | Ep. 10 - Crossed Greece, Still a Long Way
 to Go
DESCRIPTION:The journey continues across Europe. We've made progress...
 but the road ahead is still long. Expect chill vibes, scenic drives, and
 the occasional navigation regret. Travel across Europe as king of the
 road, a trucker who delivers important cargo across impressive distances!
 With dozens of cities to explore, your endurance, skill and speed will all
 be pushed to their limits.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhXKWLw5hLo
CATEGORIES:Euro Truck Simulator 2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
