LAST-MODIFIED:20260404T213100Z
DTSTART:20260401T203000Z
DTEND:20260401T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 7 - Karlshorst Command Post
DESCRIPTION:Precision gameplay continues. One shot, one chance - and
 hopefully no \"that definitely alerted everyone\" moments. In the dark
 days of the end of World War 2 amidst the ruins of Berlin, one bullet can
 change history... Elite sniper Karl Fairburne returns to the front line in
 the remaster of this award-winning stealth-action experience. Packed with
 new features, contemporary visuals and definitive content.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HHjXtlC8F1Q
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
