SUMMARY:Final Fantasy Mystic Quest | Ep. 1 - The \"Easy\" Final Fantasy...
 Is It Actually Good?
DESCRIPTION: Once you get tangled with the mob, you will forever be a part
 of the mob. At least they pay a decent salary and all you have to do is
 clean up after their dirty work, but you know what you're doing. So clean
 crime scenes, earn as much money as you can, and get ready for the next
 mission.
